1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
{\an8}<b><font color="#9CD5FF">One Pace Premium</font></b>
Keep the project alive: <font color="#a8c7fa">ko-fi.com/not6ip</font>

2
00:00:05,900 --> 00:00:07,240
Rob Lucci!

3
00:00:07,240 --> 00:00:11,990
So they're really getting rid of Vegapunk?!

4
00:00:11,990 --> 00:00:15,500
Why are you here, pigeon jerk?!

5
00:00:18,960 --> 00:00:20,540
This is a government island.

6
00:00:21,040 --> 00:00:22,210
Oh, yeah!

7
00:00:22,210 --> 00:00:24,300
We're the ones out of place!

8
00:00:25,130 --> 00:00:27,720
Who cares about that now?!

9
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:30,300
Let's hurry to the upper level, Luffy!

10
00:00:30,300 --> 00:00:32,640
What a pain in the neck!

11
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:34,560
The Straw Hats?!

12
00:00:34,560 --> 00:00:36,930
And there's Jewelry Bonney.

13
00:00:37,310 --> 00:00:40,350
But don't attack them, Lucci!

14
00:00:40,350 --> 00:00:44,820
Now that Straw Hat is an Emperor,
we need approval from the top to engage.

15
00:00:45,280 --> 00:00:46,400
He's right.

16
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:48,950
The Four Emperors come with allies.

17
00:00:48,950 --> 00:00:51,570
A skirmish could lead to a war.

18
00:00:51,570 --> 00:00:53,830
Report to the Marines at once.

19
00:00:53,830 --> 00:00:54,580
Yes, ma'am!

20
00:00:54,990 --> 00:00:57,830
I'm fully aware I shouldn't fight him...

21
00:01:01,870 --> 00:01:04,040
Take Bonney, Jinbe!

22
00:01:13,010 --> 00:01:14,390
What's going on?

23
00:01:15,140 --> 00:01:16,640
How awful!

24
00:01:18,390 --> 00:01:19,640
This girl...

25
00:01:20,310 --> 00:01:21,850
We just saw her!

26
00:01:22,310 --> 00:01:24,650
Chopper, check on her!

27
00:01:24,650 --> 00:01:25,570
Okay!

28
00:01:28,320 --> 00:01:32,570
I'm afraid we'll need
Franky's expertise instead...

29
00:01:40,410 --> 00:01:42,420
Stay out of it.

30
00:01:42,420 --> 00:01:44,420
This is government business.

31
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:52,010
She gave us lots of food to eat!

32
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:33,650
The Straw Hats are on Egghead?!

33
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:35,110
Why?!

34
00:03:35,110 --> 00:03:36,490
See?!

35
00:03:37,110 --> 00:03:40,410
Things are getting complicated again!

36
00:03:40,700 --> 00:03:45,540
Does this mean Vegapunk
figured out CP0's mission?!

37
00:03:45,540 --> 00:03:49,630
Yes. It's why they had to force their way in...

38
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:54,340
That's basically a declaration of war…

39
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:59,800
Those brats should've asked us first!

40
00:04:00,180 --> 00:04:04,060
If Vegapunk has Straw Hat on his side,

41
00:04:04,060 --> 00:04:07,020
we could suffer tremendous loss.

42
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,980
Where's Kizaru?

43
00:04:10,350 --> 00:04:12,270
He's en route to Egghead...

44
00:04:12,270 --> 00:04:16,030
for the mission we had
planned well in advance.

45
00:04:16,530 --> 00:04:20,240
Tell Lucci to wait until the Marines arrive.

46
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,160
– Yes, sir!
– Yes, sir!

47
00:04:21,910 --> 00:04:25,410
Do not permit him to fight Straw Hat!

48
00:04:28,210 --> 00:04:31,580
Intruders! Evacuate immediately!

49
00:04:31,580 --> 00:04:33,460
Evacuate immediately!

50
00:04:34,050 --> 00:04:36,460
I'll carry her, Chopper!

51
00:04:36,840 --> 00:04:39,470
Yeah, let's take her to Franky ASAP!

52
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:42,760
Luffy, come with us...

53
00:04:47,430 --> 00:04:48,640
Go ahead, guys.

54
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:01,880
Your wanted poster has a new look.

55
00:06:05,050 --> 00:06:06,550
Are you curious?

56
00:06:07,050 --> 00:06:08,560
Of course I am.

57
00:06:46,050 --> 00:06:49,680
I feel it! Feel it! Feel it! Feel it! Feel it! Feel it!

58
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,140
What's going on?!

59
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:45,190
I see...

60
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:47,030
Let's have some fun.

61
00:08:09,010 --> 00:08:10,050
Lucci!

62
00:08:17,980 --> 00:08:20,020
Hey, pigeon!

63
00:08:20,020 --> 00:08:21,230
Where are you?!

64
00:08:21,730 --> 00:08:24,320
Let's fight some more!

65
00:08:30,740 --> 00:08:33,830
You're just as flippant as ever.

66
00:08:34,450 --> 00:08:37,160
It really pisses me off.

67
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:10,030
Straw Hat!

68
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:16,740
You're not the only one who's gotten stronger!

69
00:09:19,210 --> 00:09:20,920
What's that?!

70
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:23,580
Did Rob Lucci always look like that?!

71
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:28,550
Stop, Lucci! We don't have authorization!

72
00:09:33,050 --> 00:09:34,890
What speed!

73
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:36,680
How rare that is!

74
00:09:36,680 --> 00:09:40,430
Most awakened zoan users
are robbed of their personality.

75
00:09:58,580 --> 00:10:00,250
Kiss my ass!

76
00:10:12,050 --> 00:10:13,970
Wait! Hold on, Luffy!

77
00:10:13,970 --> 00:10:16,050
Think about your position!

78
00:10:16,050 --> 00:10:17,720
This could cause a major uproar!

79
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,690
Shaka!

80
00:10:28,070 --> 00:10:30,400
Has the warrior in white appeared?

81
00:10:30,400 --> 00:10:32,150
The real one!

82
00:10:32,150 --> 00:10:34,110
But we just saw him down there!

83
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:38,080
I can't believe it!

84
00:10:38,450 --> 00:10:41,540
Tell me! What is this transformation...

85
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,750
he's undergone?!

86
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:46,130
We don't know much about it either!

87
00:10:46,130 --> 00:10:47,670
Isn't it the Gum-Gum Fruit?

88
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:54,680
There is no such fruit...

89
00:10:54,680 --> 00:10:59,390
in any of the old devil fruit encyclopedias!

90
00:10:59,390 --> 00:11:00,350
What?!

91
00:11:01,060 --> 00:11:03,430
No, no! Even if you say that...

92
00:11:03,430 --> 00:11:06,150
He's always saying "Gum-Gum."

93
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:13,240
What a magnificent figure!

94
00:11:14,070 --> 00:11:16,990
This appearance of his...

95
00:11:16,990 --> 00:11:19,990
resembles a being from old literature!

96
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:24,160
He is the spitting image of a god!

97
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:25,960
A god?!

98
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,420
This is Luffy!

99
00:11:27,420 --> 00:11:28,790
You know, an idiot!

100
00:11:30,380 --> 00:11:31,300
Indeed...

101
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:37,590
The foolish and laughable Warrior of Liberation
who brings smiles to all people!

102
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,810
Also known as...

103
00:11:42,430 --> 00:11:44,140
the Sun God,

104
00:11:44,140 --> 00:11:44,980
Nika!

105
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:50,860
Nika? I've never heard that name before...

106
00:11:50,860 --> 00:11:52,480
That's no surprise.

107
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:55,070
It was erased from history.

108
00:11:55,530 --> 00:12:00,820
But he exists as long as people yearn for him!

109
00:12:01,990 --> 00:12:05,250
All things are brought into
this world because of desires!

110
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:07,080
For example...

111
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:09,540
the devil fruits!

112
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:10,540
What?!

113
00:12:10,540 --> 00:12:12,630
The devil fruits...

114
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:18,510
are manifestations of people's
aspirations for human evolution!

115
00:12:19,050 --> 00:12:20,840
"I want to be like this."

116
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:22,810
"I want to be like that."

117
00:12:22,810 --> 00:12:26,770
The different powers represent
the diverse futures of humanity!

118
00:12:27,180 --> 00:12:30,400
And so, that unnatural status
comes with a price:

119
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:34,570
to be loathed by the sea, the mother of nature!

120
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,990
Those with powers...

121
00:12:42,950 --> 00:12:46,160
each live in different realities...

122
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:50,290
born from someone's imagination!

123
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:58,260
That is my theory!

124
00:12:59,590 --> 00:13:03,720
It's pointless to even ask whether a god exists!

125
00:13:04,930 --> 00:13:07,890
Isn't this world so fascinating?!

126
00:13:12,770 --> 00:13:16,650
These guys... Don't they
understand where they are?

127
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:20,780
This isn't a playground for
the government and pirates!

128
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:26,040
Today was meant to be my day off.

129
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:27,870
What took you so long, Sentomaru?!

130
00:13:28,750 --> 00:13:31,000
Hey, Old Man Punk!

131
00:13:31,000 --> 00:13:32,330
What should I do?

132
00:13:32,330 --> 00:13:34,210
Cipher Pol is our ally!

133
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:36,300
Pirates are our enemies!

134
00:13:37,050 --> 00:13:40,010
Am I fighting alongside CP0?

135
00:13:40,340 --> 00:13:42,930
No, not today, Sentomaru!

136
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:47,180
The thing is, CP0 is targeting me!

137
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:51,190
I'm afraid I must ask you to drive them away!

138
00:13:51,190 --> 00:13:52,440
Wait a minute!

139
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,060
That'll make me a traitor!

140
00:13:55,310 --> 00:13:56,570
You're right.

141
00:13:56,570 --> 00:13:59,780
I need you to make a choice.

142
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:01,700
Sentomaru...

143
00:14:01,700 --> 00:14:04,660
Remember that you have to repay your debts.

144
00:14:05,030 --> 00:14:06,660
The one who saved you...

145
00:14:07,030 --> 00:14:08,330
from poverty...

146
00:14:08,700 --> 00:14:10,410
was me!

147
00:14:11,290 --> 00:14:12,290
What'll it be?

148
00:14:12,290 --> 00:14:14,290
Talk about pressure!

149
00:14:22,590 --> 00:14:23,930
Is he about to strike?!

150
00:14:25,140 --> 00:14:27,390
They possess three seraphim...

151
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:30,060
We're about to be in dire straits!

152
00:14:30,970 --> 00:14:32,480
Hey, S-Bear!

153
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,690
Take one of them down!

154
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:37,270
Don't move, S-Bear!

155
00:14:38,690 --> 00:14:41,280
There's no chance, Kaku!
We have a worse hand!

156
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:42,530
S-Bear!

157
00:14:42,530 --> 00:14:44,490
Get rid of those agents!

158
00:14:50,040 --> 00:14:50,620
Retreat!

159
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,840
We're in trouble...

160
00:15:02,840 --> 00:15:03,630
Yeah...

161
00:15:04,010 --> 00:15:08,600
Sentomaru overrides our authority chips!

162
00:15:08,970 --> 00:15:09,720
Yeah.

163
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:16,600
The pacifista's orders are prioritized
based on who is issuing the orders.

164
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:20,770
First, the Five Elders are the highest priority.

165
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:25,740
The second is Dr. Vegapunk.

166
00:15:26,780 --> 00:15:28,780
The third is Sentomaru.

167
00:15:29,950 --> 00:15:34,080
Authority chip holders like us are the fourth.

168
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:38,750
No matter what we do,
Sentomaru has the final say!

169
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:43,380
Then we have to ask
the Five Elders to stop them!

170
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:44,720
It's no use.

171
00:15:44,720 --> 00:15:47,380
They must be commanded directly.

172
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:53,430
Even if it's the Five Elders, the pacifista
won't take orders through transponder snails!

173
00:15:55,390 --> 00:15:57,900
And if you give it some thought,

174
00:15:57,900 --> 00:16:01,400
taking out the seraphim means
a loss for the government!

175
00:16:01,400 --> 00:16:02,360
Damn Lucci!

176
00:16:02,730 --> 00:16:04,820
He should've looked before leaping!

177
00:16:22,460 --> 00:16:24,710
Gum-Gum...

178
00:16:26,470 --> 00:16:27,300
Mole...

179
00:16:28,260 --> 00:16:30,220
Pistol!

180
00:16:36,100 --> 00:16:37,560
Let's move!

181
00:16:37,560 --> 00:16:39,060
S-Snake!

182
00:16:39,060 --> 00:16:41,650
Get Straw Hat and the others
to the vacuum rocket!

183
00:16:42,060 --> 00:16:44,320
They need to get to the Frontier Dome!

184
00:16:44,860 --> 00:16:46,820
S-Hawk! S-Shark!

185
00:16:46,820 --> 00:16:48,820
Hold back the CP0 agents!

186
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:52,280
Chopper, I can't believe my eyes!

187
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:57,410
Those darker-skinned people look like
the former Seven Warlords of the Sea!

188
00:16:57,410 --> 00:16:58,540
Yeah!

189
00:16:58,540 --> 00:17:00,750
It's quite the resemblance!

190
00:17:00,750 --> 00:17:04,500
I can't believe they made clones out of us!

191
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:07,840
Hey! Battle-axe!

192
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:12,090
It's been a while!

193
00:17:13,100 --> 00:17:14,470
Straw Hat!

194
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:18,100
That's my weapon, not my name,
and don't act so happy to see me!

195
00:17:18,100 --> 00:17:20,310
We're enemies!

196
00:17:20,310 --> 00:17:24,020
Are you going to help
Old Man Punk get out of here?!

197
00:17:24,520 --> 00:17:26,400
Yeah, he asked me to!

198
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,230
No problem!

199
00:17:27,230 --> 00:17:30,360
I don't know if I can count on you...

200
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:32,740
I can't believe you're an Emperor now!

201
00:17:32,740 --> 00:17:35,280
And that look of yours is ridiculous!

202
00:17:42,420 --> 00:17:43,750
Hand Pistol!

203
00:17:49,550 --> 00:17:51,720
Battle-axe!

204
00:17:52,260 --> 00:17:54,600
The commander just needed to be eliminated...

205
00:17:54,970 --> 00:17:58,810
Seraphim, follow our orders!

206
00:18:00,980 --> 00:18:01,940
I'm sorry!

207
00:18:02,940 --> 00:18:04,770
I distracted you!

208
00:18:06,190 --> 00:18:07,270
Idiot...

209
00:18:08,030 --> 00:18:09,610
Don't underestimate me...

210
00:18:09,940 --> 00:18:11,610
I noticed it and...

211
00:18:19,330 --> 00:18:20,500
Damn you!

212
00:18:26,630 --> 00:18:27,710
I thought...

213
00:18:28,630 --> 00:18:29,840
I blocked it…

214
00:18:40,020 --> 00:18:41,770
How persistent...

215
00:18:42,520 --> 00:18:45,150
Pass out already!

216
00:19:24,270 --> 00:19:27,730
Your authority overrides ours,
so while you're conscious…

217
00:19:29,310 --> 00:19:32,690
we can't control the seraphim!

218
00:19:56,010 --> 00:19:58,840
Gum-Gum...

219
00:20:02,100 --> 00:20:03,850
Dawn...

220
00:20:05,930 --> 00:20:08,480
Whip!

221
00:20:17,860 --> 00:20:18,780
Lucci!

222
00:20:25,620 --> 00:20:27,160
Now is our chance!

223
00:20:27,710 --> 00:20:28,830
Luffy, hurry up!

224
00:20:28,830 --> 00:20:32,880
If you want to save this girl,
we must make haste to Vegapunk!

225
00:20:33,210 --> 00:20:36,920
I'd love to, but...

226
00:20:36,920 --> 00:20:37,590
Huh?!

227
00:20:45,270 --> 00:20:48,100
I can't stop!

228
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,570
Wh-What?!

229
00:20:56,570 --> 00:20:58,110
Where are you going, Luffy?!

230
00:20:58,860 --> 00:21:02,990
I'm spinning too much!

231
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:06,290
Come back!

232
00:21:06,290 --> 00:21:08,870
Take cover in the factory!

233
00:21:37,860 --> 00:21:40,110
The seraphim are unstoppable!

234
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:42,610
It's pointless to fight amongst ourselves!

235
00:21:42,610 --> 00:21:44,120
And they're still children.

236
00:21:44,120 --> 00:21:45,780
Their potential is terrifying.

237
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,580
Hey, Vegapunk!

238
00:21:50,710 --> 00:21:51,670
What's the matter?

239
00:21:51,670 --> 00:21:55,380
That power is what's the matter!

240
00:21:55,380 --> 00:21:57,750
See what tiny Jinbe is doing!

241
00:21:57,750 --> 00:22:00,760
Isn't that the Swim-Swim Fruit power?!

242
00:22:00,760 --> 00:22:02,260
The Swim-Swim Fruit?

243
00:22:02,260 --> 00:22:03,640
That's right!

244
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:08,680
That's my sworn brother from
the Donquixote Family...

245
00:22:08,680 --> 00:22:12,440
Senor Pink's power!

246
00:22:16,570 --> 00:22:19,990
There can't be two 
of the same fruit in this world!

247
00:22:19,990 --> 00:22:22,820
Does this mean he died?!

248
00:22:25,620 --> 00:22:27,490
Not my bro!

249
00:22:27,490 --> 00:22:29,620
So you've noticed it.

250
00:22:29,620 --> 00:22:33,000
This bro of yours is in Impel Down.

251
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:36,130
Then...

252
00:22:36,130 --> 00:22:38,800
You're saying you duplicated the devil fruit?!

253
00:22:41,260 --> 00:22:42,260
That's right.

254
00:22:42,260 --> 00:22:44,470
The devil fruits...

255
00:22:47,390 --> 00:22:50,560
can be made artificially
if they're the zoan type!

256
00:22:55,190 --> 00:22:58,320
Well, Caesar's SMILE fruits are unacceptable...

257
00:22:58,690 --> 00:23:00,900
Yeah, he can go to hell.

258
00:23:03,990 --> 00:23:07,240
The SMILE fruits are too risky.

259
00:23:07,620 --> 00:23:11,660
At best, one in ten people
will gain power by eating one.

260
00:23:11,660 --> 00:23:16,120
Everyone else without power
is forced to smile all the time...

261
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:16,960
How awful.

262
00:23:17,290 --> 00:23:19,090
Caesar...

263
00:23:19,090 --> 00:23:22,050
Just hearing that name makes me wanna puke.

264
00:23:25,010 --> 00:23:27,260
Well, putting that aside...

265
00:23:28,470 --> 00:23:32,890
I'm sure that every kind
of fruit can be replicated...

266
00:23:32,890 --> 00:23:36,480
given tons of money and time!

267
00:23:38,360 --> 00:23:41,190
Though their awakening is yet to be seen.

268
00:23:48,700 --> 00:23:52,870
I did all I could to replicate
the logia types, to no avail...

269
00:23:52,870 --> 00:23:54,080
But...

270
00:23:56,250 --> 00:23:57,750
for the paramecia types,

271
00:23:57,750 --> 00:24:00,630
I found if I can get
the user's hereditary elements,

272
00:24:00,630 --> 00:24:04,380
I can create a special blood
infusion that, when administered,

273
00:24:04,380 --> 00:24:07,010
allows someone else to have its power!

274
00:24:11,890 --> 00:24:13,180
That's...

275
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:17,230
the blood flowing through their arms!

276
00:24:18,400 --> 00:24:20,690
The green blood!

277
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:25,650
You made your own blood?!

278
00:24:29,030 --> 00:24:30,070
Love-Love...

279
00:24:32,490 --> 00:24:33,490
Mellow!

280
00:24:42,040 --> 00:24:47,340
The seraphim are the peak
of my scientific achievements!

281
00:24:51,090 --> 00:24:52,850
Ursus Shock.

282
00:25:00,730 --> 00:25:02,900
It can be said that they are...

283
00:25:04,020 --> 00:25:07,490
the strongest form of humanity ever known!

284
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:10,200
Is that why the Seven
Warlords were abolished?!

285
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:14,950
You're insane for creating
something stronger than them!

286
00:25:15,370 --> 00:25:18,160
They're essentially the Marines' weapons...

287
00:25:18,160 --> 00:25:18,910
Yeah.

288
00:25:19,370 --> 00:25:22,170
Their creation poses a threat to us.

289
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:34,680
Captain Sentomaru!

290
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:36,890
Stay away!

291
00:25:39,060 --> 00:25:40,890
He's still...

292
00:25:53,410 --> 00:25:55,700
Run, Captain Sentomaru!

293
00:25:57,450 --> 00:26:00,660
Where did your silly friend go?

294
00:26:01,290 --> 00:26:03,170
I don't know!

295
00:26:03,170 --> 00:26:04,750
And he's not my friend!

296
00:26:05,130 --> 00:26:08,210
Shut your damn, traitorous mouth!

297
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:16,140
Shave!

298
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:34,030
Straw Hat!

299
00:27:24,250 --> 00:27:25,920
You pest!

300
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:57,360
Gum-Gum...

301
00:28:06,790 --> 00:28:08,330
Dawn...

302
00:28:15,010 --> 00:28:18,470
Rocket!

303
00:28:21,350 --> 00:28:23,810
Just how powerful did he get?!

304
00:28:26,560 --> 00:28:27,730
I'm close...

305
00:28:31,190 --> 00:28:33,020
to passing out!

306
00:28:44,870 --> 00:28:46,830
This way! Hurry!

307
00:28:57,760 --> 00:28:58,510
Too slow!

308
00:29:01,260 --> 00:29:04,100
Why can't you speed things up?

309
00:29:04,850 --> 00:29:06,720
That's the vacuum rocket!

310
00:29:07,770 --> 00:29:09,100
Get on it now!

311
00:29:10,060 --> 00:29:11,730
Oh, thanks!

312
00:29:12,190 --> 00:29:14,110
You're a kind Hancock!

313
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:16,230
Thanks!

314
00:29:16,230 --> 00:29:17,860
You've been a big help!

315
00:29:17,860 --> 00:29:19,200
I-Insolence!

316
00:29:19,700 --> 00:29:22,450
I'm just following orders!

317
00:29:27,290 --> 00:29:30,250
The rocket will depart in one minute.

318
00:29:30,250 --> 00:29:32,790
Hey! Luffy!

319
00:29:32,790 --> 00:29:34,880
Hurry up!

320
00:29:38,630 --> 00:29:39,920
Oh no!

321
00:29:39,920 --> 00:29:43,140
Please refrain from rushing onto the rocket.

322
00:29:43,930 --> 00:29:45,310
Straw Hat!

323
00:29:48,060 --> 00:29:51,690
I trust you with Old Man Punk!

324
00:29:53,770 --> 00:29:54,690
Alright!

325
00:29:54,690 --> 00:29:56,110
Leave it to me!

326
00:29:58,690 --> 00:30:00,650
Stop! Go the other way!

327
00:30:03,030 --> 00:30:05,530
The doors are closing.

328
00:30:05,530 --> 00:30:06,870
Please be careful.

329
00:30:17,750 --> 00:30:19,590
We'll get him off the island...

330
00:30:21,800 --> 00:30:24,390
at any cost!

331
00:30:43,070 --> 00:30:44,280
Now departing.

332
00:30:50,620 --> 00:30:51,830
I've never been on such–

333
00:30:59,420 --> 00:31:02,300
This is quite something!

334
00:31:03,010 --> 00:31:05,470
Where am I?! Where's Vegapunk?!

335
00:31:08,260 --> 00:31:11,140
I can still fight…

336
00:31:11,140 --> 00:31:13,020
What?! Who are you?!

337
00:31:13,020 --> 00:31:14,640
That's Luffy!
A lot has happened!

338
00:31:14,640 --> 00:31:16,400
I'll tell you later!

339
00:31:16,400 --> 00:31:17,770
This is ridiculous!

340
00:31:19,860 --> 00:31:22,400
Oh, I think I'm getting
used to– Nope! Too fast!

341
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:23,690
Shut up, ship doc!

342
00:31:23,690 --> 00:31:24,450
So fast...

343
00:31:24,450 --> 00:31:27,910
How long are you gonna
be like that, Straw Hat?!

344
00:31:32,080 --> 00:31:35,460
Departing the Fabriophase,
bound for the Labophase.

345
00:31:40,130 --> 00:31:41,250
Transit duration:

346
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:43,800
thirty-two seconds.

347
00:31:45,630 --> 00:31:46,510
Arrived.

348
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:47,800
How fast!

349
00:31:47,800 --> 00:31:50,850
All subsequent rockets are canceled.

350
00:31:50,850 --> 00:31:53,140
The Labophase, Egghead.

351
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:55,100
Frontier Dome now fortified.

352
00:31:55,730 --> 00:31:57,230
Intruder alert.

353
00:31:57,230 --> 00:31:58,560
Danger.

354
00:31:58,560 --> 00:32:04,030
Researchers, please evacuate
to the factory and seal the building.

355
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,910
You're admirable in a way...

356
00:32:14,870 --> 00:32:18,040
You did fulfill your duty for Vegapunk...

357
00:32:19,210 --> 00:32:20,670
as his bodyguard.

358
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:22,380
So...

359
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:25,050
it's a shame, Sentomaru.

360
00:32:25,050 --> 00:32:29,390
The Marines told us to wait for their arrival.

361
00:32:29,390 --> 00:32:31,470
How could they take this so lightly?

362
00:32:31,930 --> 00:32:34,020
If we wait, he'll run!

363
00:32:34,930 --> 00:32:37,270
Are they really trying to kill you?!

364
00:32:37,270 --> 00:32:39,940
You're the smartest man in the world, right?!

365
00:32:40,350 --> 00:32:43,440
It would be the government's loss if you died!

366
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,650
Yes, I suppose.

367
00:32:44,650 --> 00:32:48,530
But try placing yourself in
the shoes of the higher-ups.

368
00:32:49,860 --> 00:32:54,660
My inventions have been
beneficial to the government.

369
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:58,410
Innovations using seastone in navigation technology.

370
00:32:58,410 --> 00:33:00,790
The production of cyborg animals.

371
00:33:01,420 --> 00:33:05,880
I've also studied the devil fruits
and successfully applied my findings.

372
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:08,800
I made human weapons, the pacifista.

373
00:33:09,760 --> 00:33:11,180
And...

374
00:33:11,840 --> 00:33:14,220
I completed the seraphim!

375
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:20,190
So if I moved against you as
the world's greatest intelligence, what then?!

376
00:33:20,520 --> 00:33:21,730
You're right...

377
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:23,440
I'd be pissed!

378
00:33:25,320 --> 00:33:25,940
I'd off you!

379
00:33:25,940 --> 00:33:27,150
Don't "off" him!

380
00:33:27,150 --> 00:33:32,490
I don't even have the slightest
intention of revolting,

381
00:33:32,490 --> 00:33:36,330
but those hard-headed people
firmly believe that I do.

382
00:33:36,700 --> 00:33:40,210
Well, that's just the way the cookie crumbles.

383
00:33:40,210 --> 00:33:42,920
Don't say it like it's someone else's problem!

384
00:33:43,250 --> 00:33:47,510
Then your group led by one of
the Four Emperors showed up.

385
00:33:47,510 --> 00:33:49,840
It must be fate, then!

386
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:50,380
Huh?

387
00:33:51,510 --> 00:33:53,390
You'll come aboard our ship?!

388
00:33:53,890 --> 00:33:55,390
You're most welcome!

389
00:33:56,140 --> 00:33:58,220
Super!

390
00:33:58,220 --> 00:34:01,020
Check out the General Franky!

391
00:34:01,020 --> 00:34:04,480
And the Sunny... Check her out too!

392
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:07,320
Really?! He's coming aboard?!

393
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:08,690
That's a huge burden!

394
00:34:09,070 --> 00:34:10,860
Don't worry, Nami!

395
00:34:10,860 --> 00:34:12,200
I've got you!

396
00:34:12,570 --> 00:34:14,530
I'm counting on you!

397
00:34:14,530 --> 00:34:16,450
Do your best-quasar!

398
00:34:16,870 --> 00:34:17,580
Hey!

399
00:34:17,580 --> 00:34:19,700
Why don't you free our feet, then?!

400
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:21,410
You jerk!

401
00:34:21,790 --> 00:34:24,080
Dr. Atlas!

402
00:34:24,080 --> 00:34:25,040
Oh no!

403
00:34:25,040 --> 00:34:26,500
This is serious!

404
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:28,630
We'll take care of you right away!

405
00:34:28,960 --> 00:34:32,430
Prepare to treat and repair her ASAP!

406
00:34:32,430 --> 00:34:34,720
Thank you for bringing her in!

407
00:34:34,720 --> 00:34:36,100
Leave her to us!

408
00:34:36,430 --> 00:34:37,810
Yeah, thanks.

409
00:34:37,810 --> 00:34:40,560
You guys! Where's Vegapunk?

410
00:34:41,730 --> 00:34:43,060
I know he's here!

411
00:34:43,730 --> 00:34:45,310
Tell me!

412
00:34:45,310 --> 00:34:47,230
Hey! Stop it!

413
00:34:47,230 --> 00:34:48,690
Calm down a little!

414
00:34:53,110 --> 00:34:54,860
So this is his lab!

415
00:34:56,370 --> 00:34:57,990
Cool!

416
00:34:57,990 --> 00:34:59,490
Look at this place!

417
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:02,830
That bastard!

418
00:35:03,160 --> 00:35:05,040
I will make him pay!

419
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:11,670
Bonney, where are you going?!

420
00:35:15,720 --> 00:35:19,720
If Vegapunk's response to my request
to change my father back...

421
00:35:21,390 --> 00:35:22,980
is those bugs...

422
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:29,110
I have no choice but to kill him!

423
00:35:29,110 --> 00:35:31,730
Y-You're just taking it out on him...

424
00:35:32,990 --> 00:35:34,570
Wait!

425
00:35:34,570 --> 00:35:36,110
Stop, Bonney!

426
00:35:36,110 --> 00:35:38,320
Hey! Bonney!

427
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:54,720
Our authority chips are back in effect.

428
00:35:54,720 --> 00:35:57,220
The seraphim are now ours.

429
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:59,550
The tide has turned!

430
00:36:00,260 --> 00:36:02,560
I took down one of the satellites.

431
00:36:03,930 --> 00:36:08,150
Including Vegapunk's
main body, there are six left.

432
00:36:08,150 --> 00:36:11,150
Sounds about right.

433
00:36:11,150 --> 00:36:11,980
But...

434
00:36:12,480 --> 00:36:15,190
that defense system is formidable.

435
00:36:17,450 --> 00:36:20,450
I won't let even an ant off this island!

436
00:36:20,450 --> 00:36:22,200
Destroy every ship here!

437
00:36:22,200 --> 00:36:24,160
Block off all escape routes, too!

438
00:36:25,290 --> 00:36:27,790
Don't let them get away!

439
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:43,180
So the Straw Hats are siding with Vegapunk.

440
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:47,060
That gives him a means of escape.

441
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:52,520
But it probably...

442
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:59,410
won't turn out the way he imagines.

443
00:37:01,780 --> 00:37:04,700
Proceed as planned.

444
00:37:04,700 --> 00:37:07,410
Send all available ships…

445
00:37:09,120 --> 00:37:11,210
to Egghead.

